uk.ac.ebi.pride.jmztab.model

Class SpectraRef

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ebi.pride.jmztab.model.SpectraRef

  • public class SpectraRef
extends java.lang.Object
    Peptides and small molecules MAY be linked to the source spectrum (in an external file) from which the identifications are made by way of a reference in the spectra_ref attribute and via the ms_file element which stores the URL of the file in the location attribute. It is advantageous if there is a consistent system for identifying spectra in different file formats. The following table is implemented in the PSI-MS CV for providing consistent identifiers for different spectrum file formats. This is the exact same approach followed in mzIdentML and mzQuantML. User: Qingwei Date: 29/05/13
